            <section id="mission" class="section">
                <div class="mission-header">
                    <h2>🎯 Our Mission</h2>
                    <div class="mission-content">
                        <p class="mission-primary">To ensure the safe, fair, and effective deployment of AI within Lending by establishing rigorous operational readiness standards that promote transparency, compliance, and trust.</p>
                        
                        <p class="mission-secondary">We serve as a cross-functional bridge between data science, risk, compliance, and lending teams—enabling responsible AI innovation through structured reviews, continuous monitoring, and proactive governance. Our mission is to empower lending operations with AI tools that are explainable, auditable, and aligned with both regulatory expectations and customer fairness principles.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Key Metrics to Track -->
            <section id="metrics" class="section">
                <h2>📈 Key Metrics to Track from Day 1</h2>
                <div class="metrics-grid">
                    <div class="metric-card">
 <div class="metric-target">>99%</div>                       
 <h4>Prompt Response Accuracy</h4>
                       
                        <p>Tracked through incident reporting and monitoring activities</p>
                    </div>


                    <div class="metric-card">
    <div class="metric-target">100%</div>                       
 <h4>Risk and Compliance</h4>
                    
                        <p>Ensure full adherence to Risk and Compliance standards</p>
                    </div>



                    <div class="metric-card">
        <div class="metric-target">100%</div>
                        <h4>Fair Lending Adherence</h4>
                
                        <p>Confirm no negative fair lending impact, specifically with judgmental prompts</p>
                    </div>



         <div class="metric-card">
   
                        <h4>Audit Readiness</h4>
                   
                        <p>Through extensive and organized documentation surrounding prompts, issues, and results</p>
                    </div>



