            <!-- Short-Term Plan (1-3 Months) -->
            <section id="short-term" class="section">
                <div class="plan-header">
                    <h2>✅ SHORT-TERM PLAN (1 - 3 Months)</h2>
                    <p class="plan-objectives">🎯 Objective: Stand up a lean, high-impact AI Readiness function that ensures safe, compliant, and effective use of AI in Card lending processes.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="action-grid">
                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>1. Establish Governance & Ownership</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Define scope: AI systems in underwriting, credit decisioning, procedure responses, and customer service</li>
                  
                            <li>Form cross-functional working group with reps from:
                                <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                                    <li>Credit Risk</li>
                                    <li>Compliance/Fair Lending</li>
                                    <li>Product & Underwriting</li>
                                    <li>Data Science / MLOps</li>
                                    <li>Audit / Model Risk</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>2. Create AI Readiness Documentation and Procedures</h3>
                        <p><strong>Track requirements across:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Model documentation: Version, logic, inputs/outputs, performance</li>
                            <li>Consistency: Develop AI prompt standards and guidelines</li>
 		                    <li>Testing: Craft comprehensive testing requirements for new AI solutions</li>
                            <li>Bias & fairness testing: Ensure no race, gender, religion, etc. impacts</li>
                            <li>Explainability: Transparency in decision prompt or tool logic</li>
                            <li>Resiliency: Documented plans for AI tool downtime</li>
                            <li>Audit readiness: Stored documentation of responses, issues, and prompt logic</li>
                             <li>Edge case handling: Documented strategies for managing unexpected AI behavior</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>3. Inventory Current and Upcoming AI Initiatives</h3>
                        <p><strong>Assessing AI in lending:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Prompts</li>
                            <li>Tools</li>
                            <li>LLM Integration</li>
                            <li>Upcoming AI Tools</li>
                           
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>4. Develop AI Readiness Impact Assessment</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Update impact assessment document with focus on:</strong></li>
                            <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                                   
                                    <li>AI Monitoring teams (analytics, uptime, and latency)</li>
                                    <li>Resiliency lift</li>
                                    <li>Capacity planning</li>
					<li>Procedure impacts</li>
 				    <li>Machine learning</li>
 				<li>AI vendor impacts</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>5. Establish AI Prompt/Tool to Procedure Mapping</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Create process to map existing and new AI prompts to impacted procedures</li>
                            <li>Partner with Ops Readiness to ensure procedure changes impact AI prompts</li>
                             <li>Establish visibility for AI prompts to allow for feedback</li>
                          
              
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>6. Create AI and Prompt Learning Resources</h3>
                        <p><strong>To inform stakeholders on:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Using AI responsibly</li>
                            <li>How to submit AI or prompt feedback</li>
                            <li>Tips and best practices for LLM prompts </li>
                            <li>Timeline for LLM prompt updates</li>
                            <li>How to report issues</li>
                       
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

             <div class="deliverables">
                    <h3>Deliverables by Month 3:</h3>
                    <div class="deliverables-grid">
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>AI Readiness Team Charter</strong>
                            Roles, scope, and responsibilities defined
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>Readiness Checklist</strong>
                            List of AI systems, tools, and prompts
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>AI Inventory</strong>
                            Current and upcoming AI Initiatives
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>AI Impact Assessment</strong>
                            Documented review of AI specific impacts
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>Intuitive Procedure Mapping</strong>
                            Mapping AI prompts impacted by procedure changes
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>AI Learning Resources</strong>
                            Setting expectations for AI use and prompt feedback
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Long-Term Strategy (6-12 Months) -->
            <section id="long-term" class="section">
                <div class="plan-header">
                    <h2>🚀 LONG-TERM STRATEGY (6 - 12 Months)</h2>
                    <p class="plan-objectives">🎯 Objective: Build team, reporting, monitoring, governance, and incident response capabilities.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="action-grid">
                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>1. Establish Real-Time AI Tool Monitoring Dashboard</h3>
                        <p><strong>Utilize tools like Grafana to monitor AI:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Response rate</li>
                            <li>Uptime</li>
                            <li>Latency</li>
                            <li>Errors</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>2. Build incident response team and process</h3>
                        <p><strong>When an issue is identified:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Issue is logged as a ticket (low, medium, high)</li>
                            <li>Automated alerts triggered to triage team and leaders</li>
                            <li>Resiliency plan for tool/prompt go into effect</li>
                            <li>Root cause of issue identified by triage</li>
                             <li>Issue response and resolution plan implemented and documented</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p><strong>Establish thresholds for:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Ticket resolution time</li>
                            <li>Latency</li>
                            <li>Uptime</li>
                            <li>Response rates</li>
                            <li>Errors</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>3. Report on AI Performance and Compliance</h3>
                        <p><strong>Monthly BUR sessions for:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>AI tool/prompt performance</li>
                            <li>Any Compliance or Fair Lending errors</li>
                            <li>Efficiency savings from AI tools</li>
                            <li>Upcoming AI/LLM tools and initiatives</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>4. Establish Formal AI Intake Process</h3>
                        <p><strong>Intake template outlining:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Tool/prompt description and purpose</li>
                            <li>Input and outputs defined</li>
                            <li>Used case example</li>
                            <li>Owner and reviewer</li>
                              <li>Proof of concept data</li>
                               <li>Anticipated risks</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p><strong>Optional metrics:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Number of LLM prompt injections per month</li>
                            <li>Impact if tool fails</li>
                            <li>PI or PCI included</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>5. Build Audit Ready Edge-Case and Compliance Library</h3>
                        <p><strong>That will include:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Detailed errors and incidents</li>
                            <li>Root causes</li>
                            <li>Steps taken to resolve</li>
                            <li>Proof of resolution and testing evidence</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="action-item">
                        <h3>6. Develop Resiliency and Communication Plan for AI Downtime</h3>
                        <p><strong>Resiliency plans to consider:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>FTE required without AI/LLM tool</li>
                            <li>Process and procedures accessibility</li>
                            <li>Customer and business impact</li>
                             <li>Trigger conditions for manual intervention</li>
                               <li>Testing cadence for bringing tool back online</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p><strong>For communication:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                           <li>Automated alerts</li>
                            <li>Clear escalation paths</li>
                            <li>Clear AI tool status</li>
                                    <li>Expected resolve timeframe</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    
                </div>

                <div class="deliverables">
                    <h3>Deliverables by Month 12:</h3>
                    <div class="deliverables-grid">
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>Real-Time AI Dashboard</strong>
                            Alerts on latency, uptime, and errors
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>Incident Response Team</strong>
                            Defined roles, responsibilities, and processes
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>Reporting Dashboard</strong>
                           Present performance on monthly BUR
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>AI Intake Process</strong>
                            For new AI tools and prompts
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>Edge-Case and Compliance Library</strong>
                            For audit readiness and compliance
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <strong>Resiliency and Communication Framework</strong>
                            Detailed plans for AI tool downtime
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Future-Term Strategy (24+ Months) -->
            <section id="future-term" class="section">
